Overview

This dashboard shows Threat overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Threat logs from Prisma Access.

It highlights the top actions performed by the firewall and identifies the applications associated with detected threats. It categorizes threats by application subcategory and visualizes their occurrence over time by severity level. The dashboard also lists the top security policy rules.
